title: Matt Helders Drummer of the Arctic Monkeys
description: Shapel Lacey sits down with Arctic Monkeys drummer, Matt Helders to discuss the progression from his band's early days until now.  Matt also breaks down Shapel's drumming ability. Plus Shapel tries not to bring up Oasis every time he opens his mouth.
